  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to verify the effectiveness of Trafermin (recombinant human basic fibroblast
      growth factor) in stimulating regeneration of periodontal tissue lost by periodontitis and to
      evaluate the safety of such stimulation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
